</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Tesla 車 CAM 捉刮車者，清楚錄低過程＋犯人長相</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/31/tesla-sentry-mode/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tesla-sentry-mode</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 31 Dec 2021 10:50:27 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sentry Mode]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tesla]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079112</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>各款 Tesla 車身皆裝有多個鏡頭以監控行車路況，而司機可於停車時把車輛設定為 Sentry Mode（哨兵 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>各款 Tesla 車身皆裝有多個鏡頭以監控行車路況，而司機可於停車時把車輛設定為 Sentry Mode（哨兵模式），將靠近車輛的人錄低。此項能力除了有助抓小偷外，更可以找出刮車者。</p><p>英國有女司機把小狗放在車上，因害怕別人逗她的狗，故意將車停泊在車位之間的白線上（讓其他人避免將車停泊於旁邊）。但後來一輛 Model 3 在此車的相鄰位置停泊，對此不滿的女司機因此用鑰匙刮花 Model 3。 Model 3 的車主卻透過 Sentry Mode 將該名女司機的惡下錄低。下圖為車輛拍攝得到的畫面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.19.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079159" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39-675x580.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39-675x580.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39-1047x900.jpg 1047w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39-768x660.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.15.39.jpg 1368w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05-1280x755.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05-768x453.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05-1536x906.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-31-16.16.05.jpg 1582w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>根據片段提供的線索，Model 3 車主找到了刮車者的名字、長相、職業、年齡。Model 3 車主後來報警，把車輛錄下的片段交給警方。警方迅速根據車牌登記資料找到該名刮花車身的女車主。最後刮花別人車輛的人需要向 Model 3 的車主賠款 1078.83 英磅（約港幣約 1.13 萬元）。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63638"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0fJFM_3Y6F0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://udn.com/news/story/6812/5993010">聯合新聞網</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
