</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>不明無人機停警車前不動，警員上前執起未見駕駛員</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/31/droneontheroad/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=droneontheroad</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 31 Dec 2021 10:28:47 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079174</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>前日（12 月 30 日）下午  5 時，在旺角海街近旺角道交通燈前，有一部無人機停在警方的衝鋒車前。此情形並不 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>前日（12 月 30 日）下午  5 時，在旺角海街近旺角道交通燈前，有一部無人機停在警方的衝鋒車前。此情形並不常見，引來不少路人停下來圍觀拍照。警方見狀，把無人機帶回警署，惟未有看見無人機操控員。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079180 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270036221_456933276017487_975917862290301324_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270036221_456933276017487_975917862290301324_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270036221_456933276017487_975917862290301324_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270036221_456933276017487_975917862290301324_n.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=456933592684122&amp;id=100438938333591">香港 • 社實</a> facebook 專頁</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079183 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270303375_456933862684095_2848570266206218884_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079182 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/271117912_456933972684084_2565362558046773674_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079181 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270894315_456934009350747_717443657399669228_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=456933592684122&amp;id=100438938333591">香港 • 社實</a> facebook 專頁</p><p>無人機停在衝鋒車後約一分鐘，有警員落車了解，並徒手拾起，放在警車前方。再過一會，警員把無人機放在附近店舖貨物之上，管理貨物的店員對此表示不滿。警員隨後再移動無人機至衝鋒車內副駕駛位，並送往警署。有網民擔心航拍機內藏炸彈，建議警方日後需更小心行事。</p><p>根據《 1995 年飛航（香港）令》（香港法例第 448C 章）第 48 條訂明任何人士不得罔顧後果或疏忽地引致或容許飛機（包括無人機）對他人或財產安全構成危險，違者可遭檢控。一經定罪，可處罰款及監禁兩年。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079176 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270100193_456933309350817_1533919820857034946_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270100193_456933309350817_1533919820857034946_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270100193_456933309350817_1533919820857034946_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270100193_456933309350817_1533919820857034946_n.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079177 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270772963_456933342684147_3554413350111025515_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270772963_456933342684147_3554413350111025515_n-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270772963_456933342684147_3554413350111025515_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270772963_456933342684147_3554413350111025515_n.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1079178 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270068473_456933382684143_4391056958624677495_n-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/270